OL,3,CNo charges over ice hockey star
OL,4,CJohnson's death
OL,6,FAn ice hockey player who was arrested
OL,7,Fover the death of opponent Adam
OL,8,FJohnson during a match will not face
OL,9,Fcriminal charges, the Crown
OL,10,FProsecution Service (CPS) has said.
OL,12,FNottingham Panthers forward Johnson,
OL,13,F29, was fatally injured in a collision
OL,14,Fwith Sheffield Steelers player Matt
OL,15,FPetgrave at Sheffield's Utilita Arena
OL,16,Fon 28 October 2023.
OL,18,FHe died of a neck injury.
