OL,6,FPetgrave was arrested in November 2023
OL,7,Fon suspicion of manslaughter and has
OL,8,Fbeen on bail since.
OL,10,FOn Tuesday, the CPS confirmed he would
OL,11,Fface no further action.
OL,13,FDeputy Chief Crown Prosecutor Michael
OL,14,FQuinn said: "This was a shocking and
OL,15,Fdeeply upsetting incident. The CPS and
OL,16,FSouth Yorkshire Police have worked
OL,17,Fclosely together to determine whether
OL,18,Fany criminal charges should be brought
OL,19,Fagainst the other ice hockey player
OL,20,Finvolved.
