OL,6,F"Following a thorough police
OL,7,Finvestigation and a comprehensive
OL,8,Freview of all the evidence by the CPS,
OL,9,Fwe have concluded that there is not a
OL,10,Frealistic prospect of conviction for
OL,11,Fany criminal offence and so there will
OL,12,Fnot be a prosecution.
OL,14,F"Our thoughts remain with the family
OL,15,Fand friends of Adam Johnson."
