OL,4,CJohnson's death
OL,6,FJohnson's death - witnessed by
OL,7,Fthousands of people inside the arena
OL,8,Fin Sheffield - was initially described
OL,9,Fby the Panthers as a "freak accident".
OL,10,FIt led to an outpouring of grief from
OL,11,Ffans around the world.
OL,13,FThe announcement by the CPS brings an
OL,14,Fend to 18 months of uncertainty for
OL,15,FPetgrave, who had started a
OL,16,Ffundraising campaign to support his
OL,17,Flegal case.
