OL,6,FIn a message on a crowd-funding page,
OL,7,Fhe wrote that he had no insurance
OL,8,Fcover following his arrest and added:
OL,9,F"The time and costs involved in the
OL,10,Flegal investigation and potential
OL,11,Fcourt proceedings are difficult for me
OL,12,Fto cover on a privately funded basis.
OL,14,F"This is especially challenging
OL,15,Fbecause my UK Visa has expired,
OL,16,Fpreventing me from working as a
OL,17,Fprofessional ice hockey player while I
OL,18,Fcontinue to need legal assistance."
