OL,6,FIn a statement the Elite League (EIHL)
OL,7,Fsaid: "We note the recent update from
OL,8,FSouth Yorkshire police that no charges
OL,9,Fwill be bought against Matt Petgrave
OL,10,Ffollowing the death of Adam Johnson in
OL,11,FOctober 2023.
OL,13,F"Our thoughts remain with everyone
OL,14,Finvolved in the accident, and player
OL,15,Fsafety and welfare remains our top
OL,16,Fpriority."
